        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards-grid">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-wrapper bg-purple">
                <span class="icon">ðŸŽ“</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Study Abroad</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">
                Discovery, scholarships, and visa support all in one place.
                Reduce the chaos of multiple portals.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-wrapper bg-orange">
                <span class="icon">ðŸ’¼</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Global Employment</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">
                Up-skilling, internships, and profile building tailored to
                international standards.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-wrapper bg-pink">
                <span class="icon">ðŸ”„</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="card-title">One Profile</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">
                Everything synchronized. Your loans trigger visa support, your
                grades trigger internship matches.
            </p>
